<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Error</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #171a21;
            color: #c4d1da;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            background: url('https://steamcommunity-a.akamaihd.net/economy/image/-9a81dlWLwJ2UUGcVs_nsVtzdOEdtWwKGZZLQHTxH5rd9eDAjcFyv45SRYAFMIcKL_PArgVSL403ulRUWEndVKv4gJaEAQ07dl1U4r_9KQZh0KGZcDhGu4zuwYbbkqfxa7qJlzkBusR33LuRrd6i3RqemzSFSdPyqA?size=300x180f') no-repeat center center fixed;
            background-size: cover;
        }
        .error-container {
            text-align: center;
            background: rgba(23, 26, 33, 0.9);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            color: #c4d1da;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 2em;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            color: #66c0f4;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            color: #c4d1da;
        }
        a {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #66c0f4;
            border: 1px solid #66c0f4;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s, color 0.3s;
        }
        a:hover {
            background-color: #66c0f4;
            color: #171a21;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="error-container">
    <h1>Oops!</h1>
    <p>Something went wrong. Please try again later.</p>
    <a href="/all-games">Go back to All Games</a>
</div>
</body>
</html>
